snippet.title: Spreadcheat Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the wonderful corporate word of the 90's and commit tax evasion by solving interesting Excel puzzles in SpreadCheat, the latest in Windows 3.1 technology!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2966550/SpreadCheat/
